data.description: Welcome to this stunning property! Step inside and be greeted by a cozy fireplace, creating a warm and inviting ambiance. The natural color palette throughout the home promotes a sense of tranquility and harmony. The kitchen boasts a nice backsplash, adding a touch of elegance to the space. Flexibility is key with additional rooms, providing endless possibilities for your lifestyle needs. The primary bathroom offers a separate tub and shower, perfect for a relaxing soak or an invigorating rinse. Good under sink storage in the primary bathroom ensures a clutter-free environment. Enjoy the comfort of a new HVAC system, providing optimal temperature control. With fresh interior paint, the home feels rejuvenated and ready for its new owner. Don't miss the chance to make this your dream home!
